F27%2F181708_fb32c18abbdb4fd05b16f455a3b201fc.jpg&h=1d3ef8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩乜？<br />\n<br />\n係迷宮入面找大佬打<br />\n<br />\n用角色既技能<br />\n<br />\n範圍大係好用但cost 相對高，所以有一個高cost就夠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/182032_9c56bbfd57a5f925c08153e11d01b25f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F182032_9c56bbfd57a5f925c08153e11d01b25f.jpg&h=08c55b14&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用男女主角有得俾你突滿上100lvl，勁過未突既5星<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/182038_c82731e13066040ac482065aa3ae60b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F182038_c82731e13066040ac482065aa3ae60b7.jpg&h=2f67c5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/182043_87f72a74614612b0c19b91f56e49267f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F182043_87f72a74614612b0c19b91f56e49267f.jpg&h=95c76b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得協力同打公會龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有分真假5星？<br />\n<br />\n角色名有個+，就係最高既5星<br />\n<br />\n不過其實係技能分別<br />\n<br />\n所以起手冇別要一定要有+5星"}]}